{"tid":412851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三分鐘漫畫揭祕！日本應召女郎的真實心聲...","createTime":"2017-09-25T04:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T04:32:01.000Z","uid":25345,"like":70,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"db7adffd639846ea3e45c458d185fa4448ecbc17","tid":412851,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:21:20.000Z","msg":"日本風俗種類相當多，今天要為大家介紹的是大部分日本風俗店&mdash;&mdash;ヘルス。ヘルス就是所謂的半套店，玩法差不多，但算法差很多&hellip;有些店的算法是包幾個基本項目 通常都會包含深吻、口X、打奶泡、親吻全身之類的這些&hellip;但要在規定時間內要玩幾次皆可，唯獨不可的就是本番&mdash;&mdash;即真做。<br />\n<br />\n日本法律是將賣淫活動以「生殖器接觸」作為依據，在日本叫「本番」，這在日本法律中是明令禁止的，雖然日本女性中也有一些人從事暗娼活動，但數量相當少。　必須要說明一點，在日本做「本番」的妓女，以外國人居多，日本女性只是少數，特別是東亞、東南亞的女性基本佔了一大半兒。<br />\n<br />\n一般這種還有分店家裡就有小房間的 或是要到附近飯店的 外出的又稱デリヘル，但即使叫到摩鐵去，也不能真做的噢！雖然口頭上說不願意這種通常加價一些就可以本番（真做）&hellip;但也有美眉不願意的&hellip;不能勉強。<br />\n<br />\n我們來看看下面這齣漫畫，再現應召女的真實心境！<br />\n▼兩人開始脫衣服<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/o0opRm6t.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fo0opRm6t.jpg%3FkFQ&h=c73351a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/2aVB3bMt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2F2aVB3bMt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=0bbe2a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼大叔很噁唉，但沒辦法，性服務業嘛！<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/b9nyodnt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fb9nyodnt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=c4a7657c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/ZoEFoAEt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FZoEFoAEt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=c02ef2d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼即使客人有性病，也不得不滿足需求..<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/r1rU1g9t.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fr1rU1g9t.jpg%3FkFQ&h=99924156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼有些時候客人還要求本番！<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/p8mkAlQt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fp8mkAlQt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=3e0a3e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼給完錢爽後還不忘記數落你一番！<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/KpohcHRt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FKpohcHRt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=8ea096b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5dcd94d097ca36110ebbf768c7261f83c2a4e3a","tid":412851,"uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"還有就是風俗女最忌諱的就是客人愛上自己，因為事情會變得很麻煩。有一位應召女曾在twitter說過一句話。別把我們這行和普通的服務業搞混好不好。難道因為理髮師給你剪過頭髮你就愛上理髮師了嗎？一樣的道理！<br />\n<br />\n還有，在棉被裡的時候，她們會關心客人「不會冷吧？」客人的回答都是「不冷。妳也不冷吧？」她們笑著說，這只是一種營業的方式，就如同理髮師在給你洗頭的時候會問你「沒有癢的地方吧？」你的回答竟是「不癢，你也不癢吧？」同樣搞笑滑稽！<br />\n<br />\n我們看下面一段，客人愛上應召女時的反應...<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/UyzPUq2t.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FUyzPUq2t.jpg%3FkFQ&h=43b488e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/xv7q6rSt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fxv7q6rSt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=c369ced2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/gLoIn2kt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FgLoIn2kt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=810bca0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/M0RxQkKt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FM0RxQkKt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=b4deaa4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.imgs.cc/img/sXiuqpht.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FsXiuqpht.jpg%3FkFQ&h=f9c4e48c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.imgs.cc/img/FSSPZEjt.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FFSSPZEjt.jpg%3FkFQ&h=460d12f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你以為這樣就結束了嗎？當客人愛上自己的時候，竟然出高價出到20萬日幣（新台幣5萬左右）要跟心愛的應召女來次本番（真做）！但她們的心情是什麼？<br />\n<br />\n&darr;<br />\n&darr;<br />\n&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"http://s1.imgs.cc/img/xv7nya6t.jpg?kFQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2Fxv7nya6t.jpg%3FkFQ&h=3cd85f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還有就是這些半套店的應召女郎最喜歡的一類客人就是「短、快、小」，50分鐘的時間內10分鐘就發射牛奶的話對他們來說簡直就賺到！她們有時候會和客人有些許交流，客人會說些很自卑的話「我的很小」「我很不受歡迎」，她們都必須微笑拼命否定「才沒有很小呢」（心裡想著確實很小有賺到！）「您一定很受歡迎吧？」之類的話奉承..."},{"pid":"a9324750addd1d5648c6d3a547c2a1411016bd91","tid":412851,"uid":21896,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"又係呢套漫畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0751f72d41e4fb57d2f8f72098da799b9b809c2","tid":412851,"uid":17642,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"又係吸血大耳窿呢本漫畫"},{"pid":"20aae7377f3b179f339cf0654a5b97e6e0e30c5e","tid":412851,"uid":90123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:38:31.000Z","msg":"幾好睇"},{"pid":"999efe7c53b9c6e7e76c61a80229879b846dcc71","tid":412851,"uid":24345,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:42:06.000Z","msg":"吸血大耳窿起香港唔紅冇天理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc8f6871c4b0a8a1261a7c3507948c4600dac7d","tid":412851,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:45:41.000Z","msg":"咁香港呢"},{"pid":"327e76247dd4643f3fb7dd0930606b6b3307dbb5","tid":412851,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"仲有無多啲？？"},{"pid":"17a2b533ded6c3ca92bbd6b803a0dff01350b098","tid":412851,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係內容農場"},{"pid":"797f5275e43a8c1ec4149697f813eab736934d83","tid":412851,"uid":47359,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成年前都有</span>"},{"pid":"be627f8483